    SequenceElementFactory<T>

    public class AbstractElementFactory<T extends SequenceElement>
extends java.lang.Object
implements SequenceElementFactory<T>
    This is universal serialization/deserialization factor for SequenceVectors serialization. It will work for any <T extends SequenceElement> that doesn't breaks simple POJO rules.
